<template>
  <n-config-provider :theme="darkTheme">
    <n-global-style />
    <n-result status="403" title="503 服务器娘挂了哦" description="要不要听听歌呢">
      <template #footer>
        <n-button type="primary" @click="msg">找点乐子吧</n-button>
      </template>
    </n-result>
  </n-config-provider>
</template>
<script>
import { darkTheme } from "naive-ui";
import { defineComponent } from 'vue'
import { useMessage } from 'naive-ui'

export default {
  setup() {
    return {
      darkTheme,
      msg
    };
  },
};

const msg = defineComponent({
  setup () {
    const message = useMessage()
    return {
      handleClick () {
        message.info('Button Clicked')
      }
    }
  }
})
</script>
